ygData.messageBody:
Nice to know gold works - but plat works too - in fact - I have used only
plat.

Now - does anyone know for sure if that Jbootie gnome will cough up booties
for plat or do you have to crawl around with 3250 gp? Anyone feel that
lucky to find out?

Sylly
